            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><rs>Papa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Popes">Gregorio VII</persName>, su richiesta di <persName
                            key="#Bishops">Guilielmo</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/86"
                            >Populoniensis</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>, conferma allo stesso presule episcopatum
                        predicte Populoniensis ecclesie cum omni iure suisque pertinentiis. Cuius
                        episcopatus fines et possessiones sunt videlicet locus qui dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/348">Alma</placeName> et exinde usque in <rs
                            key="#Sea">mare</rs> et in <rs key="#Islands">insulam</rs> que vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Islands" ref="#places/378">Elba</placeName> et inde in
                        mare in <placeName ref="#places/379">Sedium</placeName> supra ipsum mare et
                        exinde iusta in <placeName>Stafile Auricausi</placeName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/380"><rs key="#Rivers">rivum</rs>
                            Sabuli</placeName> et exinde in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential #Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#places/381">Salam <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/263"
                                >Allonis</persName>
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducis</rs></placeName> inde vero in <placeName
                            ref="#places/382">Aslaito</placeName> et exinde in<placeName key="#Vici">
                            <rs key="#Vici">Vicum</rs> Montanini</placeName> et inde ad
                            <placeName>Sanctum Petrum</placeName> in quo persido inde vero ad
                            <placeName ref="#places/383">Sanctum Iohannem in <rs key="#Gualdi"
                                >Gualdum</rs> donni <rs key="#Emperor/king">regis</rs></placeName>
                        et ad <placeName>Sanctum Philippum</placeName> et inde ad <placeName
                            ref="#places/85">Montem Viridem</placeName> et inde ad <placeName>Fontem
                            Fontignani</placeName> per <placeName ref="#places/384"
                            >Faianum</placeName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/385">Paganicum</placeName> in <placeName>Aquam
                            Caldulam</placeName> et ad <placeName>Campum Mustiuole</placeName> inde
                        vero ad <placeName>Sussianum</placeName> et exinde ad
                                <placeName><placeName>Viniale</placeName></placeName> et inde in
                            <placeName>Scannelli</placeName> inde vero in
                            <placeName>Fraginetum</placeName> et exinde in <placeName>Campum
                            Arenensem</placeName> et inde in <placeName>Campum Gagoni</placeName>
                        inde vero in <placeName>Arenam</placeName> et exinde in
                            <placeName>Libistellum</placeName> et inde in <placeName
                            ref="#places/386">Serule</placeName> inde vero in <placeName
                            ref="#places/387">Pancie</placeName> et exinde in <placeName
                            ref="#places/388">Butre</placeName> et inde in <placeName
                            ref="#places/389">Planizzule</placeName> inde vero in
                            <placeName>Suppatre</placeName> et exinde ad
                            <placeName>Argali</placeName> et inde in <placeName><rs key="#Mountains"
                                >montem</rs> Danazzonem</placeName> inde vero in
                            <placeName>Querqueta</placeName> et exinde in
                            <placeName>Termine</placeName> et inde in
                            <placeName>Cerbaiuola</placeName> inde vero in
                            <placeName>Iusciani</placeName> et exinde in <placeName
                            ref="#places/390">Lama de Arcle</placeName> fine ad <placeName>Pratum
                            Firmi</placeName> et inde in <placeName ref="#places/391"
                            >Terrige</placeName> fine <placeName ref="#places/392">Petram
                            Albam</placeName> et inde in <placeName ref="#places/393"
                            >Ercle</placeName> qui est iuxta suprascriptam Almam vel quecumque alia
                        episcopalia iura. Proibisce illicita exactione vel usurpatione di re,
                        imperatori, duchi, conti, vescovi e abati, alcuna persona magna et parva.
                        Concedentes et corroborantes eidem Populoniensi ecclesie denominate quidem
                            <placeName key="#Islands #Decima" ref="#places/378">Elbam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Islands">insulam</rs> cum omnibus locis et ecclesiis <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimationibus</rs> omnique iure rerum illuc pertinentium.
                        Similiter etiam et reliquas <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebes</rs> cum
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Villages/settlements">villis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Castle">castellis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> cultis et incultis secundum
                        ambitum terminorum et diffinitionis, que in antiquis privilegiis eidem
                        ecclesie collatis invenitur ut prelibatum est. Concesso per manus del <rs
                            key="#Cardinals">prete cardinale</rs> e bibliotecario Sancte Romane
                        Ecclesie <persName>Pietro</persName>. Scrive: <persName>Ranieri</persName>
                        scriniarius S. Romane Ecclesie. Datum <placeName>Lateranis</placeName>. </ab>
                        </div>
